                <note rend="inline" type="source">890g.01/220: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dawes</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-10-19T14:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 19, 1929—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>277. Department’s No. 259, September 26, 11 a.m. Is there likely to be delay in
                    receiving the Iraqi communication regarding Article 28 of the Public Education
                    Law?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
